      <li>Municipal lots and pay stations - arrive early on weekends and holidays.</li>
<li>Start 60-90 minutes before sunset for the best light.</li>
<li>Build in buffer for peak season traffic.</li>
    </ul></div>
    <div class="card"><h2>Typical Guest Counts</h2><ul>
      <li>Great for 2-40 guests; seating add-ons available with most packages.</li>
    </ul></div>
